item.title: By: Judith
item.dc:creator: Judith
item.description: <p>With the weekend approaching fast you can be sure of another hangover after the Big BBQ, the views look nice, anyone good with freezers our has packed up! thanks to mum and Matt's mum our food being saved! We're waiting to see of it works after today the ice cubes are frozen this morning I guess that's a good sign??!! </p>
